text: tae anak del ban brate b tde tam kar ylprom pi a l laoh ( daoy minban yk phnek namuoy nei chyophond daoy khosachbab) dauch anak del ban neamk nouv kar khoeng pi a l laoh( daoy ban yk phnek na muoy nei chyophond daoy khosachbab) der ryyte? haey kanleng snaknow robsa ke ku thanonork haey vea chea kanleng vilotralb da akrak bamphot
